// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0210 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 3bbcbf64-2edf-51e3-936d-23032b04f851

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
